title.narrative: Improving access to healthcare in northern Uganda

description.narrative: This activity (Improving access to healthcare in northern Uganda) is a component of Post-Conflict Development in Northern Uganda reported by FCDO, with a funding type of 'Procurement of Services' and a budget of £12,170,824. This component benefits Uganda, and works in the following sector(s): Health policy and administrative management, Basic health care, Reproductive health care. , with the following implementing partners: DAI Global Health. The start date is 15-12-2010 and the end date is 30-11-2015.
